t id; omit to use all active accounts.'}, 'cost_method': {'type': 'string', 'description': 'Cost method: fifo or avg (default: fifo).', 'enum': ['fifo', 'avg']}, 'include_positions': {'type': 'boolean', 'description': 'Whether to include full positions in snapshot output (default: false).'}, 'include_risk': {'type': 'boolean', 'description': 'Whether to include risk summary block (default: true).'}, 'as_of': {'type': 'string', 'description': 'Optional snapshot date in YYYY-MM-DD format (default: today).'}}}}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'get_capital_flow', 'description': "Get main-force (主力) capital flow data for an A-share stock. Returns today's net inflow, 5-day and 10-day cumulative inflows, and top sector-level capital flow rankings. Only supported for A-share individual stocks (not ETFs, indices, HK, or US stocks).", 'parameters': {'type': 'object', 'properties': {'stock_code': {'type': 'string', 'description': "A-share stock code, e.g., '600519'"}}, 'required': ['stock_code']}}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'analyze_trend', 'description': 'Run comprehensive technical trend analysis on a stock. Fetches historical data from database or data source. Returns MA alignment, bias rates, MACD status, RSI levels, volume analysis, support/resistance levels, and a buy/sell signal with a score (0-100).', 'parameters': {'type': 'object', 'properties': {'stock_code': {'type': 'string', 'description': "Stock code to analyze, e.g., '600519'"}}, 'required': ['stock_code']}}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'calculate_ma', 'description': 'Calculate moving averages (MA5/10/20/30/60/120/250 or custom periods) for a stock. Returns each MA value, price bias %, and whether price is above each MA. Also returns overall MA alignment (多头/空头/混合).', 'parameters': {'type': 'object', 'properties': {'stock_code': {'type': 'string', 'description': "Stock code, e.g., '600519'"}, 'periods': {'type': 'string', 'description': "Comma-separated MA periods to 