ether to include risk summary block (default: true).'}, 'as_of': {'type': 'string', 'description': 'Optional snapshot date in YYYY-MM-DD format (default: today).'}}}}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'get_capital_flow', 'description': "Get main-force (主力) capital flow data for an A-share stock. Returns today's net inflow, 5-day and 10-day cumulative inflows, and top sector-level capital flow rankings. Only supported for A-share individual stocks (not ETFs, indices, HK, or US stocks).", 'parameters': {'type': 'object', 'properties': {'stock_code': {'type': 'string', 'description': "A-share stock code, e.g., '600519'"}}, 'required': ['stock_code']}}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'analyze_trend', 'description': 'Run comprehensive technical trend analysis on a stock. Fetches historical data from database or data source. Returns MA alignment, bias rates, MACD status, RSI levels, volume analysis, support/resistance levels, and a buy/sell signal with a score (0-100).', 'parameters': {'type': 'object', 'properties': {'stock_code': {'type': 'string', 'description': "Stock code to analyze, e.g., '600519'"}}, 'required': ['stock_code']}}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'calculate_ma', 'description': 'Calculate moving averages (MA5/10/20/30/60/120/250 or custom periods) for a stock. Returns each MA value, price bias %, and whether price is above each MA. Also returns overall MA alignment (多头/空头/混合).', 'parameters': {'type': 'object', 'properties': {'stock_code': {'type': 'string', 'description': "Stock code, e.g., '600519'"}, 'periods': {'type': 'string', 'description': "Comma-separated MA periods to calculate (default: '5,10,20,30,60,120,250'). E.g., '5,10,20,60'"}, 'days': {'type': 'integer', 'description': 'Number of trading days to fetch history for (default: 120)'}}, 'required': ['stock_code']}}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'get_volume_analysis', 'description': 'Analyse volume-price relationship for a stock. Returns volume ratios, average volume on up vs down days, volume trend (expanding/shrinking), and pattern interpretation (量价配合/背离). Useful for confirming trend strength and detecting distribution or accumulation phases.', 'parameters': {'type': 'object', 'properties': {'stock_code': {'type': 'string', 'description': "Stock code, e.g., '600519'"}, 'days': {'type': 'integer', 'description': 'Number of recent trading days to analyse (default: 30)'}}, 'required': ['stock_code']}}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'analyze_pattern', 'description': 'Detect candlestick and chart patterns in recent price history. Identifies: Doji, Hammer, Shooting Star, Morning/Evening Star, Engulfing, Double Bottom, upward breakout, box oscillation, and more. Returns pattern list with type (bullish/bearish/reversal) and strength.', 'parameters': {'type': 'object', 'properties': {'stock_code': {'type': 'string', 'description': "Stock code, e.g., '600519'"}, 'days': {'type': 'integer', 'description': 'Number of recent trading days to scan (default: 60)'}}, 'required': ['stock_code']}}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'get_market_indices', 'description': 'Get major market indices (e.g., Shanghai Composite, Shenzhen Component, CSI 300 for China; S&P 500, Nasdaq, Dow for US). Provides market overview.', 'parameters': {'type': 'object', 'properties': {'region': {'type': 'string', 'description': "Market region: 'cn' for China A-shares, 'us' for US stocks (default: 'cn')", 'enum': ['cn', 'us']}}}}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'get_sector_rankings', 'description': 'Get sector/industry performance rankings. Returns top N and bottom N sectors by daily change percentage. Useful for sector rotation analysis.', 'parameters': {'type': 'object', 'properties': {'top_n': {'type': 'integer', 'description': 'Number of top/bottom sectors to return (default: 10)'}}}}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'get_skill_backtest_summary', 'description': 'Inspect backtest data for a speci