ck code, e.g., '600519'"}, 'days': {'type': 'integer', 'description': 'Number of recent trading days to scan (default: 60)'}}, 'required': ['stock_code']}}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'get_market_indices', 'description': 'Get major market indices (e.g., Shanghai Composite, Shenzhen Component, CSI 300 for China; S&P 500, Nasdaq, Dow for US). Provides market overview.', 'parameters': {'type': 'object', 'properties': {'region': {'type': 'string', 'description': "Market region: 'cn' for China A-shares, 'us' for US stocks (default: 'cn')", 'enum': ['cn', 'us']}}}}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'get_sector_rankings', 'description': 'Get sector/industry performance rankings. Returns top N and bottom N sectors by daily change percentage. Useful for sector rotation analysis.', 'parameters': {'type': 'object', 'properties': {'top_n': {'type': 'integer', 'description': 'Number of top/bottom sectors to return (default: 10)'}}}}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'get_skill_backtest_summary', 'description': 'Inspect backtest data for a specific skill when skill-scoped stats exist. Provide skill_id for a targeted lookup; use get_strategy_backtest_summary for overall metrics. When skill-scoped rollups are unavailable, returns an informational response instead of fabricating metrics.', 'parameters': {'type': 'object', 'properties': {'skill_id': {'type': 'string', 'description': "Skill identifier, e.g. 'bull_trend'."}, 'eval_window_days': {'type': 'integer', 'description': 'Evaluation window in days (default: 30). How many trading days after signal to evaluate.'}}, 'required': ['skill_id']}}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'get_strategy_backtest_summary', 'description': 'Legacy alias returning the overall backtest performance summary without triggering new backtests.', 'parameters': {'type': 'object', 'properties': {'eval_window_days': {'type': 'integer', 'description': 'Evaluation window in days (default: 30). How many trading days